title: Gateway Black Friend
description:
Are you white? Do you want a more diverse group of friends?  Well, introducing the Gateway Black Friend!

Written by Jasmine Pierce

Featuring  Tessa Hersh, Willy Appelman, Michael Delisle, Maya Deshmukh, Tristan Griffin and Chrissy Shackelford
Directed by Matt Gehring
Shot by Thursday Shoots
Edited by Phillip Russell
